-- Russia’s First-Half Gold Output Falls 2.4% to 79.2 Metric Tons
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-08-06T13:13:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-06/russia-s-first-half-gold-output-falls-2-4-to-79-2-metric-tons.html
Russia’s first-half gold output fell
2.4 percent to 79.2 metric tons, led by a decline at  Kinross
Gold Corp. (K) ’s mine in the Chukotka region, the country’s Gold
Producers’ Union said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
